Bury Them Deep - Any Phase: Each time William spends a monster trophy, he may decide to return it to the box instead of placing it back in the monster cup.','4','6','1 Skill','1 Skill','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'The Story So Far: If all the world truly was a stage, then William Yorick felt he had a bit part at best. After studying for years to become a Shakespearean actor, he found that dramatic monologues didn''t put bread on the table. So, desperate for work, he had accepted a job as a gravedigger.
